# How-To
To use this, you have to download [Tampermonkey] (https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/tampermonkey/dhdgffkkebhmkfjojejmpbldmpobfkfo?hl=en) for Google Chrome, and for Mozilla Firefox, you have to use [Greasemonkey] (https://addons.mozilla.org/en-GB/firefox/addon/greasemonkey/). I don't know if there are any add-ons for other browsers. If so, message me or make an Issue about it. Click [**This**] () and click Install

# Thanks,
## MeowMeowCat
